description: Located in the heart of East Nashville's 5-points, I Dream of Weenie is known both for its quirky modified VW bus and yummy signature charcoal-grilled weenies.  Get yours to-go or grab a blanket to enjoy a picnic on the lawn.I Dream of Weenie is now located at 113 South 11th Street, behind Fanny's House of Music and across from Pied Piper Creamery - just around the corner from its original home.All standard menu items such as the favorite "Rebel Yelp" and a rotating menu of creative Daily Dreams are served on a fresh-baked locally made artisan bun, and are available on your choice of a premium all-beef, turkey, or tofu weenie.
name: I Dream of Weenie
